messages.message:
Slightly different type of comment - load time of aihub.instabase.com (http://aihub.instabase.com) is significantly longer than 4 seconds and is getting flagged by Google as a poor URL. Poor URLs get scored down in search results. Ways around this:

• Improve load times if possible
• Create an easy quick load landing page and don't index the product page
@Subash  your recent changes should improve this, right? i know they haven’t been deployed to aihub.instabase.com (http://aihub.instabase.com) yet
Yes, There should be considerable improvement. The changes include reducing the asset size to load the AI Hub home page.  These changes will be deployed in upcoming release.
